title: 8 mile 720 p Blue ray mp4
description:
This is YIFI's version of 8 mile converted to mp4 (Apple TV)720p. It does look better on TV than a regular PC but the quality is still good.

If you actually have an Apple TV but your WiFi doesn't reach your living room here's what you could do :

Get a cheap android smartphone ( mine's a $ 70 alcate), and switch on personal hotspot. This created a powerless Wifi that you can still connect with both the Apple TV and your laptop/other Apple product. This would allow you to airplay without problems. I don't really know how it works but I'm sure it does :)
